      <title>古代文物表明澳大利亚的仪式已延续 12,000 年</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2437808-ancient-artefacts-suggest-australian-ritual-endured-for-12000-years/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
