      <title>在深度冷冻和辐射下存活的苔藓可以在火星上生存</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2437761-moss-that-survives-deep-freeze-and-radiation-could-live-on-mars/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
